import React from 'react' import Text from '../components/Text' function DriverandGNSS({long , lat , acc ,velo }) { return (
Driver AND GNSS

LAT : {lat}

LON : {long}

ACC : {acc} M

RTK : OK

VEL : {velo} m/s

DRIVE 1 : 1200

DRIVE 2: 1200

DRIVE 3 : 1200

DRIVE 4 : 1200

DRIVE 5 : 300

DRIVE 6 : 300

DRIVE 7 : 300

DRIVE 8 : 300

) } export default DriverandGNSS
